                           <locus target="#2r-23r-23v-39v">-2r, 23r, 23v, 39v</locus>
                           <desc>Marginalia</desc>
                           <note>Notes marked Tuḥfa, ǧīm, ǧīm ǧīm, fā’ tā’ bā’, bā’ ǧīm ḥā’ lām and Taqrīr</note>
                           <note>
